column4: <content>Very important for Good Shepherd. Françoise Popelier, Image des luttes religieuses dans la peinture des anciens Pays-Bas, Bulletin Musées Royaux de Belgique, XVIII, 1969, pp. 121-138. A painting connected with the Bruegel engraving containing explanatory inscriptions & portrait of Philip II, Calvin, etc.</content>

<part_of.title>Good Shepherd: Stridbeck, fig. 54, probably developed from Bruegel's engraving late 16th century, Stridbeck, fig. 54. See also Stridbeck, p. 256 for Unfaithful Shepherd.</part_of.title>
<keyword>Brussel, Koninklijke Musea voor Schone Kunsten van België</keyword>
